00:01:48,087 --> 00:01:49,714
Just in case, I bought the flyers

36
00:01:49,714 --> 00:01:53,514
from all kinds of eating places that were in our mailbox.

37
00:01:53,514 --> 00:01:55,714
Shall we try them?

38
00:01:55,714 --> 00:01:58,097
Anything that looks good?

39
00:01:58,097 --> 00:02:00,099
Specialty Pizza "Colossoo",

40
00:02:00,099 --> 00:02:02,101
Miso cutlet "Tsubouchi",

41
00:02:02,101 --> 00:02:05,114
Hiroshima-style okonomiyaki "Kondo"...

42
00:02:05,114 --> 00:02:07,514
None of which I'm in the mood for.

